examples.en: I will forever be indebted to you for this wonderful experience.
We are indebted to her for her help.
We are deeply indebted to Dr Allen.
I would be indebted to any alert readers for corrections of factual material.
The movement is philosophically indebted to Rousseau.
She thereafter forever felt indebted to the producer for giving her her lucky break.
He was indebted to the pioneering work of John Dewey.
